VJ Innovative Software Solutions Private Limited is a Private Limited Company providing industry-ready software training, customized digital solutions, and customer support services. The company specializes in software education, e-commerce software development, and BPO services.

It offers practical training programs in Python, Java, Web Development, Full Stack, AI/ML, Data Science, and Cloud Computing through classroom, online, and workshop-based learning, helping students and professionals gain job-ready skills.

For businesses, the company develops customized websites, mobile apps, backend systems, inventory and order management tools, payment integrations, CRM solutions, chatbots, and automation tools to support e-commerce operations. It also delivers multilingual customer support services including call centre's, live chat, email, and ticketing solutions. The company serves students, professionals, retail owners, e-commerce firms, and corporate clients, focusing on innovation, quality, and growth through technology.
